{"id":772,"date":"2019-07-28T22:37:03","date_gmt":"2019-07-28T22:37:03","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/bhide.net\/?page_id=772"},"modified":"2026-01-02T07:33:47","modified_gmt":"2026-01-02T12:33:47","slug":"completed-case-histories-of-medical-advances-as-of-july-2019","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/completed-case-histories-of-medical-advances-as-of-july-2019\/","title":{"rendered":"Links to Working Papers on Transformational Medical Advances"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Our case-histories (<a href=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/index.php\/practical-knowledge\/medical-advances-cases\/\">which we started writing started in 2014)<\/a> reflect (and helped produce) ideas in my <a href=\"https:\/\/papers.ssrn.com\/sol3\/papers.cfm?abstract_id=3666503\">Note on Productive Knowledge <\/a>(and in this <a href=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/papers%20and%20articles\/bhide_limiting_medical_innovation.pdf\">Critical Review essay<\/a>).<\/p>\n<p>An HBS elective, <a href=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/index.php\/practical-knowledge\/lessons-from-transformational-medical-advances\/\">Lessons from Transformational Medical Advances<\/a> (LTMA) which I taught in the Spring of 2021 connected the case histories, propositions about productive knowledge, and the Critical Review essay.<\/p>\n<p>Links to the working papers that were adapted for the course are below.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/papers.ssrn.com\/sol3\/Delivery.cfm\/3863155.pdf?abstractid=3863155\">&#8220;Chimeric Antigen Receptor (CAR) T-Cell Therapy.&#8221;\u00a0<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9 and Datar)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3679640\">&#8220;Cephalosporins.&#8221;<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3679645\">&#8220;Tamoxifen.&#8221;\u00a0<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3866769\">SSRIs and Non-SSRIs: (Prozac<\/a>).&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"https:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3427408\">Coronary Artery Bypass Grafting<\/a>.&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Villa)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3427400\">&#8220;Ultrasound.&#8221;<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3427247\">&#8220;Magnetic Resonance Imaging.\u201d<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3424129\">&#8220;Mammography.&#8221;<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3429278\">Laparoscopy<\/a>.&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Bowler, Datar)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3429950\">HIV Tests and AIDS Treatments<\/a>&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3429959\">Eradicating Helicobacter Pylori Infections to Treat Ulcers<\/a>.&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/ssrn.com\/abstract=3429986\">Gastrointestinal Endoscopy<\/a>.&#8221; ((Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p>&#8220;<a href=\"https:\/\/papers.ssrn.com\/sol3\/Delivery.cfm\/3429976.pdf?abstractid=3429976&amp;type=2\">Computed Tomography<\/a>.&#8221; (Bhid\u00e9, Datar, Stebbins)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hbs.edu\/faculty\/Pages\/download.aspx?name=21-132.pdf\">Fecal Transplants<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9 and Datar)<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hbs.edu\/faculty\/Pages\/download.aspx?name=24-055.pdf\">Dame Cicely Saunders and the Hospice Movement<\/a> (Bhid\u00e9 and Datar)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our case-histories (which we started writing started in 2014) reflect (and helped produce) ideas in my Note on Productive Knowledge<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":1,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"colormag_page_container_layout":"default_layout","colormag_page_sidebar_layout":"default_layout","footnotes":"","_link